The antenna and the rectifier were fabricated forming the rectenna (Fig. 10). At 868 MHz the simulated (sml) rectifier’s efficiency and the measured (msr) rectenna’s efficiency versus power input and power density for output load of 2193 Ω\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
